    public enum Layer

    Defines the layers (grids) that a density tile may hold. [Future selves of us might question why we only go up to 2020, but unlikely we will use this code base in 2020.]

        public static Layer inferFrom(org.gbif.api.vocabulary.BasisOfRecord bor,

        Utility to determine to which layer an occurrence record belongs. This assumes that the record is plottable, so no verification on the coordinates is performed.
